'''Abersaith Canyon''' was a large canyon on [[Corulag/Legends|Corulag]]. At its widest, Abersaith spread several [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] wide and ran almost twenty-five kilometers in length. The canyon also contained the [[Abersaith Aviary]].<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

